          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "As I",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "mentioned",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "earlier, EV’s a pretty quiet cars (almost all silent) and a joy to listen to audio in.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In fact, just today I found myself listening to a ‘peaceful piano playlist’ on Spotify, a twist on my normal morning routine of listening to podcasts on end.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Then, quite abruptly, a suped-up Mitsubishi Eclipse swerved past me, its muffler buzzing with commotion.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "As if it couldn’t get any more disturbing, we ended taking the same turn down the two-lane side-street, a route just long enough to spoil the better half of “Ambre” by Nils Frahm.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The lesson? I want a quieter car, he’s clearly content with a louder one.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Marketing starts with choosing your people: Those who want more or less? Expensive or cheap? Louder or quieter? Pompous or modest? Bright or restrained?",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "\n",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s a mistake to assume that different people don’t want different things.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
